Name: Sif
Description: Sif was born a second generation goddess of Asgard and eventually became Thor's lover.
FirstComicDescription: Will Jane Foster pass the test of the gods? Odin allows Jane to accept the mantle of a goddess...but only if she can overcome the trials of Asgard. Lady Sif catches Thor's eye.
